Another workshop called 'Skunkhour,' will teach attendees about the science behind beer flavouring.

'If Good Beer Wheaty Yeastie could be encapsulated in one word, it would have to be spooning,' Wheatsheef Hotel co-publican Jade Flavell said.

The festival runs from Thursday 15 May until Monday 19 May.

